<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Referral Form Submission Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: #28a745;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .info-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .info-table td {
        padding: 8px 0;
      }
      .info-table td.label {
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 40%;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Referral Form Submitted Successfully</h2>
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for submitting the <strong>Referral Form</strong>. We’ve successfully received your referral details.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our team will review your submission and get back to you shortly with further details or next steps.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you didn’t submit this form, please ignore this email.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">&copy; SAA Accounting. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
